      "61": "kai outoi anebhsan apo qelmeleq arhsa caroub hrwn iemhr kai ouk hdunasqhsan apaggeilai oikous patriwn autwn kai sperma autwn ei apo israhl eisin",
      "62": "uioi dalaia uioi twbia uioi nekwda exakosioi tessarakonta duo",
